    <string-array name="muavin_quotes">
        <item>Fines hurt, Muavin saves lives.</item>
        <item>Take it easy champion, your destination isn\'t running away.</item>
        <item>Eyes on the road, not the gas. I\'m here.</item>
        <item>I see the radar before it sees you.</item>
        <item>Watch the needle if you love your wallet!</item>
        <item>Fast gets there early, slow gets there safely.</item>
        <item>Traffic fine? Not my style.</item>
        <item>The roads are yours, the caution is my job.</item>
        <item>Maybe rein in those horses under the hood a bit.</item>
        <item>Radars lie in wait, Muavin spoils the game.</item>
        <item>Is your seatbelt on? Check it!</item>
        <item>Don\'t speed, think of those waiting for you.</item>
        <item>Don\'t let the road end with a ticket.</item>
        <item>Be careful all the time, not just when you see a radar.</item>
        <item>The passion for speed is nice, but fines are sad.</item>
    </string-array>

